&lt;p&gt;Everyone has their GSoC proposal in. Madhu's went in after a bit of late drama about her application status being set to 'withdrawn' in mentor's dashboard. Intervention by _ke fixed things up, and everyone lived happily ever after :)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Apr 6&lt;/h3&gt;
