&lt;p&gt;Wrote good amount of GSoC proposal. awjr says it's in good shape. Sumanah suggested I fix more bugs, so on the lookout. Had a skype convo with awjr about the current, twisted manual workflow that I'm going to help automate.&lt;/p&gt;
